text: Warm friendly church members. Good preaching.
Nice church for all morning service and youth service

I recommend this place of worship. Definitely a place where you are being ministered and encouraged by the preaching of the Living Word.

There are children services for all ages.

Visit the official website for more details for services in different  languages and time.

The place is not crowded yet cosy. The nearest MRT Station (Beauty World) is less than 100 metres away.

Recommended by a church friend when I need to host an award presentation event and was very please with the setup and infrastructure.

Did not know if was converted from an old movie theatre. Highly recommended!
Was there to catch a movie of the life of Eric Liddell. Enjoyed the movie. Organised by Scripture Union.
